# PLP Bookstore - MongoDB Assignment (Week 1)

## Overview
This project demonstrates the fundamentals and advanced techniques of MongoDB.  
It includes database setup, CRUD operations, advanced queries, aggregation pipelines, and indexing for performance optimization.  

The database used is `plp_bookstore` with a single collection `books` containing 10+ sample book documents.

---

## ðŸ“‚ Files Included
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `insert_books.js` | Script to insert 10+ sample book documents into the `books` collection. |
| `queries.js` | Contains all MongoDB queries including CRUD, advanced queries, aggregation pipelines, and indexing examples. |
| `screenshot.png` | Screenshot from MongoDB Compass/Atlas showing the `books` collection with inserted data. |

